name: Sales Higher
overview:
Sales Higher is a sales assessment test for employers to select applicants with the right personality to succeed in a competitive sales role.

The Sales Higher assessment evaluates and scores applicants according to their Drive, Independence, Assertiveness, Extroversion, and Conscientiousness. The best sales people in the world demonstrate strength in each of these areas.

Once the applicant completes the online sales test, it is “graded” almost instantaneously and the results are presented to employers in an easy to evaluate color coded format for each sales trait measured plus an overall recommendation of whether to move forwards with the applicant.
